[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy charged after shotgun seized at Nuneaton school

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A teenage boy has been charged after a shotgun and ammunition were seized at a Warwickshire school.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
He has been charged with possession of a firearm and ammunition with intention to endanger life and possession of an article with a blade on school premises.
Police arrested the boy after being called to Higham Lane School in Nuneaton on Tuesday.
The boy, from Nuneaton, will appear at Warwickshire Magistrates' Court later.
